{"Title":"炝腰花的做法","Primary":["猪腰500g"],"Auxiliary":["食盐适量","酱油适量","鸡精适量","料酒适量","胡萝卜适量","冬笋适量","黑木耳适量","芝麻油适量","花椒油适量"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.猪腰自中间平剖开。 ","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20110611/ff219e12fab2f9a5e968607e9dc59b44.jpg","2.用刀子将中间的腰骚片掉，这里是骚气的源泉，所以一定要弄干净。","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20110611/e86c3307638fec120e957a8db62f1484.jpg","3.先斜着切，不要切断。","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20110611/44a9d8c087adbffb8eace11c5dbc9c93.jpg","4.反过来，竖着切，将其切成麦穗状。 ","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20110611/d810407d76dceac024382f25eb43ad50.jpg","5.切成小块。 ","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20110611/c696faac7f83d9cfe440fd230d0f2f4c.jpg","6.将其泡入水中，去除血水。","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20110611/0c2cec207d47e0b69830a8340ed9b30a.jpg","7.胡萝卜和冬笋切菱形片。黑木耳泡发。","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20110611/d92356139ae7e023200ab5544e579bd8.jpg","8.将黑木耳洗净，揪成小片，连同胡萝卜和冬笋片一起焯熟。","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20110611/dcfd8a9486b3ddab683839a12bfcc779.jpg","9.将腰花焯熟。腰花易熟，不用煮太久，影响口感。 ","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20110611/705e853a59355474d4d78b9819770b97.jpg","10.将焯水的蔬菜和猪腰一起浸入凉水中过凉。捞出控干水分。","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20110611/c4eef9b1b8c453bd76a5745972f1d91e.jpg","11.用料酒、酱油、盐、鸡精、香油调汁。 ","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20110611/09ff48974a80cedafe468fe8c7d7cc79.jpg","12.倒入料汁，搅拌均匀。","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20110611/b840ebeb8e1739762d2123e64a971766.jpg","13.锅内放油，放10几粒花椒，炸成花椒油。 ","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20110611/6f70f0c035a04cba0d2d4d19d3172cda.jpg","14.将炸好的花椒油倒入盆内，用滤网将花椒粒虑出。 ","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20110611/70bd955c4b8efaad886bb0abb9ba1caf.jpg","15.搅拌均匀，装盘即可。 ","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20110611/2594b20ab3dab45913a7a43fad6ff23d.jpg"]}